research_municipality_step.notes: Providence Village, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government. The Town Council is composed of a Mayor and six Council Members elected under a Place System. While Jeff Doramus is listed as Deputy Mayor Pro Tem, and other Council Members are explicitly assigned to Places 1, 2, 3, 4, and 6, it is inferred that Jeff Doramus holds Place 5 to complete the six Council Member positions as per the town's charter.
